        {
            "title": "以為只衝擊軟件股？AI 恐慌擴散至傳統行業　物流貨運股單日挫逾一成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近日軟件股受人工智能（AI）相關憂慮，股價節節下跌，如今拋售名單再添一員，就是物流與貨運板塊，物流及貨運營運商 C.H. Robinson（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:CHRW;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CHRW/\">CHRW</a>）及 Universal Logistics（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:ULH;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/ULH/\">ULH</a>）周四（12日）股價均挫一成以上，原因是一家名不見經傳、原本生產卡拉OK機的公司，宣布推出新 AI 工具，聲稱可在不增加人手的情況下提升貨運量，有分析員指 AI 帶來的變革不僅影響軟件業，更將加速波及其他板塊。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"以為只衝擊軟件股？AI 恐慌擴散至傳統行業，物流貨運股單日挫逾一成。（C.H. Robinson）\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"638\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PMdh0bojhVqHIKR2HjFYyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/737207f0-0868-11f1-bf9f-2dd80427b076\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">以為只衝擊軟件股？AI 恐慌擴散至傳統行業，物流貨運股單日挫逾一成。（C.H. Robinson）</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[%E2%80%A6]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=s1kW4IOA4iZoKC480912&amp;uuid=n71xwVw3nRy25ecw0845&amp;uuid=cSM0RfGjBMAB6hoF0568&amp;uuid=DuIuMOWACtzsBO9v0182&amp;uuid=xB4uJWWz1ECOpprK0310&amp;uuid=tI3bFLm2SkvtQBBV0990&amp;uuid=fxfksXClqFqTK6wd0763&amp;uuid=ybkNYokd68f51swq0786&amp;uuid=FMZsYcaovPDiRiEn0238&amp;uuid=DBJmJP7M8dIuFAza1268&amp;uuid=UfT13nXCr4cvW6En0657&amp;uuid=PXZAVgzDtTubfzB50492&amp;uuid=vKvKMdPxcax8uKVB0858&amp;uuid=b9lwBa9QJpW1nDGE0691&amp;uuid=vlRWlWNhKBZhiAgc0737&amp;uuid=uYLODeNHhsonQhC20339&amp;uuid=pifNpXs63jptqi5H0279&amp;uuid=qp3YUzwMSdJD6vlL0645&amp;uuid=rSYcc3skG3GLP5390333&amp;uuid=1R5wK6mBCx7lpBL30982&amp;uuid=uv2JhhemlLAEcqZS0245&amp;uuid=HPOVGtqDrX1VPYoP0134&amp;uuid=Vbm9qeF23UbKFUwV0740&amp;uuid=Vo0ggtFtaaFjlbAR0293&amp;uuid=Ahrs29aW8UxKfVmp0319&amp;uuid=KY0FM5IlGv5VyL3b0194&amp;uuid=soNUUI0W39s6NWaQ0319&amp;uuid=fF9FZQ3iPNdsnDWO0733&amp;uuid=NOj3FXU9Tx70uoXQ0820&amp;uuid=MhCeryurfIarguZ70925&amp;uuid=dJI9g1zfikEQ3MMB0696&amp;uuid=MoePYhrruAkd1rRs0006&amp;uuid=3uloGdI2IxSVhxco0690&amp;uuid=0g1fhWirY5eHWOo00348&amp;uuid=pB3zJNo2pNKJnGDT0310&amp;uuid=5uff9nLVdntja92R0991&amp;uuid=lVoURqEo4b225m8c0686&amp;uuid=r1VKOeN31MjW7xI90753&amp;uuid=q0kOLvuspTV2UEMx0255&amp;uuid=Lz5GIZHDJSDguZTU0988&amp;uuid=8KB2pkDP7CtTJEfn0031&amp;uuid=e0jKA61WpqkKrpy20289&amp;uuid=M5Bw1vIAZqmSrjxV0292&amp;uuid=SLaEgDglJvf5GRMv0638&amp;uuid=d7EEH4xTRhgNOlXW0638\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>原生產</strong>卡拉OK機 研發 <strong>AI 引發震盪</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Algorhythm Holdings（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:RIME;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/RIME/\">RIME</a>）周四表示，其平台正「將貨運管理由勞動密集、手動流程，轉型為高度自動化、由智能主導的系統」，並聲稱可帶來「4 倍員工生產力提升」；Algorhythm 股價在消息公布後一度飆升 79%，最終收市升 29%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5f5d687b-3473-4aba-9e70-e2e7d6da7dfb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得注意的是，該公司直至 2025 年第三季仍經營卡拉 OK 機業務，其後將業務出售予 Stingray Group（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:STGYF;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/STGYF/\">STGYF</a>），再轉型為以 AI 為核心的貨運解決方案公司。收市時，公司市值仍不足 1,000 萬美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">即使消息來源只是規模細小的公司，但物流板塊的劇烈波動亦拖累行業龍頭，包括馬士基（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:MAERSK-B.CO;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MAERSK-B.CO/\">MAERSK-B.CO</a>）及 UPS（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:UPS;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/UPS/\">UPS</a>）股價下跌，惟跌幅較小，另一家物流公司 Hub Group（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:HUBG;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/HUBG/\">HUBG</a>）股價則下跌約 6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jefferies 分析師 Jeff Favuzza 於 2 月 12 日致客戶報告中指出：「目前市場表面下最明顯的主題，不僅限於科技股，而是整個市場，只要出現與 AI 有關的標題，投資者便傾向先拋售、後提問。」他補充：「我們也希望知道這種情況何時停止／觸發因素是甚麼。」</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>不止物流 金融與地產股亦受波及</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">LPL Financial 首席股票策略師 Jeff Buchbinder 在電郵評論中表示：「過去數周，資本市場面對眾多變數。」他列舉因素包括「股市板塊輪動、金屬與商品價格波動」、以及「地緣政治緊張、全球央行決策及大型企業業績」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事實上，周四物流股的下跌，緊接金融服務股與地產股前一輪拋售。此前，一家同樣規模不大的公司 Altruist 推出 AI 驅動的稅務軟件，令 Charles Schwab（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:SCHW;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/SCHW/\">SCHW</a>）、Raymond James（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:RJF;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/RJF/\">RJF</a>）、Compass（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:COMP;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/COMP/\">COMP</a>）及 Jones Lang LaSalle（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:JLL;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JLLS/\">JLL</a>）等股份下挫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟件股拋售亦持續。AppLovin（APP）股價周四下跌 19%，儘管公司周三公布的經調整每股盈利及收入均優於市場預期，管理層亦嘗試將 AI 描述為正面催化劑。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>AI 憂慮暫未影響貨幣政策預期</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四主要股指亦受壓，科技股為主的納斯達克綜合指數（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:^IXIC;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC/\">^IXIC</a>）跌 2%，標普 500 指數（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:^GSPC;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC/\">^GSPC</a>）及道瓊斯工業平均指數（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:^DJI;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI/\">^DJI</a>）分別下跌約 1.5% 及 1.3%。不過，目前這類輪動式板塊拋售主要局限於股市，尚未明顯影響市場對貨幣政策走向的討論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Macquarie 全球策略師 Thierry Wizman 在報告中指出，若恐慌情緒持續升溫，AI 憂慮或會開始對聯儲局構成實質壓力。聯儲局內部的「鷹派」或會基於通脹仍具黏性及就業市場穩健而支持加息；而「鴿派」則可能傾向讓經濟保持較高增長，以推動生產力提升，抵消 AI 取代職位所帶來的憂慮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wizman 寫道：「上周開始的『AI 恐慌交易』仍令交易員對美股風險持審慎態度。若情緒進一步惡化，政策是否應維持緊縮的『舉證責任』，或將落在鷹派身上。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"AI不止衝擊軟件行業，更開始影響傳統產業。資料圖片。 (AP Photo/Damian Dovarganes)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pNhd7XqmXI0pMS7dHh_E1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0Mg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/35be9fe0-0151-11f1-bdfe-4da384bb473f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">AI不止衝擊軟件行業，更開始影響傳統產業。資料圖片。 (AP Photo/Damian Dovarganes)</figcaption></div></figure><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>AI 已成企業披露中的重大風險</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">AI 威脅亦開始反映於企業財務披露之中，根據 Conference Board 於 10 月進行的一項研究，標普 500 成份股中，近四分之三公司在文件中將 AI 列為重大風險，遠高於 2023 年僅 12% 的比例。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構表示，這一轉變凸顯 AI 由試驗階段迅速發展為業務關鍵系統，董事會與管理層亦正為聲譽、監管及營運風險作準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">UBS 策略師 Matthew Mish 近日在報告中指出，投資者正尋找各個板塊的任何疲弱跡象，因為市場愈來愈相信快速演進的 AI 模型將顛覆大範圍經濟活動，他表示：「2 月由 AI 顛覆主導的拋售，是基於一個合理信念：AI 帶來的變革不僅影響軟件業，更將加速波及其他板塊。」他亦指「AI 顛覆發生的時間仍難以確定，而不確定性的迷霧短期內難以消散。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>撰文：Jake Conley（Yahoo Finance 即時財經新聞記者）<br/>原文：</strong><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:AI fears spark sell-off in shipping, freight stocks in sign ‘every corner of the market’ is an AI target;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ai-fears-spark-sell-off-in-shipping-freight-stocks-in-sign-every-corner-of-the-market-is-an-ai-target-212041918.html\"><strong>AI fears spark sell-off in shipping, freight stocks in sign ‘every corner of the market’ is an AI target</strong></a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%AA%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E8%82%A1%EF%BC%9Fai-%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C%E6%93%B4%E6%95%A3%E8%87%B3%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD-%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E8%B2%A8%E9%81%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E6%8C%AB%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E6%88%90-232126141.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 07:26:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜納指大跌2%　老麥可樂創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜納指大跌2% 老麥可樂創新高\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RcxQoOmYfJ_IPV84uo0u5w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/dc346560-0860-11f1-9d7c-b43ec6542e78\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜納指大跌2% 老麥可樂創新高</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周四急挫，道指下跌約1.3%，即逾660點，標普500指數下跌1.6%，納指跌幅最大，下挫超過2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金期貨下跌3%，比特幣亦回落至約65,000美元水平，跌幅同樣逾3%，顯示投資者風險胃納下降，投資者關注明天公布的消費物價指數數據，以尋找對減息前景有否線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場正憂慮哪些行業最易受到人工智能顛覆的影響，科技股普遍下跌，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:思科;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CSCO/\">思科</a>股價下跌超過 12%，而<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Amazon;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">Amazon</a>及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:蘋果;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL/\">蘋果</a>均大幅回落，其中蘋果下跌約 5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-48015999-0afd-427b-bdd3-2dc7d76ef9aa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月12日（星期四）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌669.92點或1.34%，報49,451.98點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌108.71點或1.57%，報6,832.76點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌469.32點或2.03%，報22,597.15點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約3月期油;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約3月期油</ins></a> 收報62.91美元一桶，跌1.72美元或2.66%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報4,937.5美元一盎司，跌161美元或3.16%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報65,338.66美元, 跌2,184.76美元或3.23%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.104厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透社引述消息人士報道，在中美兩國元首4月會晤之前，特朗普政府將擱置一系列針對北京的關鍵技術安全措施，這些措施包括禁止中國電信（728）在美國開展業務，以及限制向美國數據中心出售中國設備，似乎有意製造有利會議的環境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國全國房地產經紀人協會(NAR)數據顯示，美國現有住宅銷售在今年1月按月下降8.4%，年化銷售率降至391萬套，遠低於市場預期的418萬套。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">科技股無運行，業績亮麗的傳統股成為逆市奇葩。餐飲股<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:麥當勞;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MCD/\">麥當勞</a>在美國銷售額於第四季度實現兩年多以來的最快增長，季度營收達70億美元，同比增長9.5%，超出預期1.6億美元。股價收市升2.7%，創歷史新高。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:可口可樂;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/KO/\">可口可樂</a>業績後繼續強勢，同樣再創歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洞洞鞋<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Crocs;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CROX/\">Crocs</a>公布業績，在新產品提振需下，去年第四季淨利潤1.05億美元，經調整每股盈利2.29美元，遠高於市場預期的1.91美元。公司對本季盈測亦勝預期，刺激股價急升，收市升19%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由軟銀集團支持的日本QR碼支付巨頭PayPay，計劃下月在美國納斯達克交易所上市。知情人士透露，公司的市值預計將超過3兆日圓(約196億美元)。軟銀計劃出售約10%的股份。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C%E7%B4%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C2-%E8%80%81%E9%BA%A5%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-222507237.html",
