            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C-ai%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%94%93%E5%BB%B6-%E6%80%9D%E7%A7%91%E6%85%98%E5%B4%A9%E8%B6%8512-%E9%81%93%E7%93%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB%E8%BF%91700%E9%BB%9E-214347785.html",
